data.title: George Harrison
data.meta_description: An original design doodle for an Apple Records LP label by George Harrison, pencil and felt pens,  circa  1969, with self-portrait George Harrison sitting under an apple tree, with handwritten album title  George Harrison , publisher credit  BMI .  Harrisongs  and gag track listings in black ink  1 Hello Dolly, 2 Perfida, 3 Mrs Harrison, 4 Ballad of Eddie Veale, 5 Fuck Of Dolly 6 Ballad of Eddie Klein 4 in. (10.1 cm.) diam.
